Very likely.

00:17:36.080 --> 00:17:37.000
I think all this

00:17:37.200 --> 00:17:38.720
is deliberately arranged by the killer.

00:17:38.720 --> 00:17:40.050
At Ma Jinguang's house,

00:17:40.120 --> 00:17:41.040
I found out he actually bought

00:17:41.040 --> 00:17:42.570
many identical backpacks.

00:17:42.640 --> 00:17:44.160
If he was really online

00:17:44.160 --> 00:17:45.480
illegally selling explosives,

00:17:45.480 --> 00:17:46.160
for safety,

00:17:46.440 --> 00:17:48.400
they definitely wouldn't trade face-to-face.

00:17:48.400 --> 00:17:50.440
They'd just leave the stuff at a drop-off spot.

00:17:50.440 --> 00:17:50.880
So,

00:17:50.960 --> 00:17:52.040
he used the backpacks

00:17:52.040 --> 00:17:53.440
to hold the explosives he sold.

00:17:53.440 --> 00:17:54.720
After getting the explosives,

00:17:54.720 --> 00:17:56.400
the killer threw the backpack at the crime scene

00:17:56.400 --> 00:17:57.130
to frame him.

00:17:57.360 --> 00:17:59.090
But the backpack is a variable.

00:17:59.760 --> 00:18:02.040
If Ma Jinguang had bought different styles of backpacks,

00:18:02.040 --> 00:18:03.840
the framing would hardly succeed.

00:18:03.840 --> 00:18:06.280
Unless the killer had been tracking him

00:18:06.480 --> 00:18:08.160
and even sneaked into his house.

00:18:08.160 --> 00:18:09.400
Since the killer was dead set

00:18:09.400 --> 00:18:10.920
on making it look like Ma Jinguang did it,

00:18:10.920 --> 00:18:12.400
he would definitely make Wang Hongjia

00:18:12.400 --> 00:18:13.330
appear near him.

00:18:13.880 --> 00:18:14.480
This way,

00:18:14.840 --> 00:18:15.360
Zhang Biao

00:18:15.360 --> 00:18:16.320
becomes his victim,

00:18:16.320 --> 00:18:17.040
and Wang Hongjia

00:18:17.040 --> 00:18:18.680
was kidnapped by him to the cabin.

00:18:18.680 --> 00:18:19.640
It all connects.

00:18:19.800 --> 00:18:22.200
That's probably how the killer planned it.

00:18:22.480 --> 00:18:23.960
But there was an accident.

00:18:24.200 --> 00:18:25.060
What accident?

00:18:26.440 --> 00:18:27.640
I'll confirm it soon.

00:18:27.800 --> 00:18:28.800
I'm almost there.

00:18:29.080 --> 00:18:30.010
Where did you go?

00:18:30.360 --> 00:18:30.890
The mine.

00:18:31.080 --> 00:18:32.140
It's getting dark.

00:18:32.440 --> 00:18:33.680
The mine could be dangerous.

00:18:33.680 --> 00:18:34.360
Be careful.

00:18:34.480 --> 00:18:35.120
I'm coming over now.

00:18:35.120 --> 00:18:35.440
Okay.

00:18:35.440 --> 00:18:36.520
Come over as soon as possible.